 "data": "@startuml

' Исключения
class FailedToBoardWagonException {
 + FailedToBoardWagonException(name: String)
}

class IceCreamDepletedException {
 + IceCreamDepletedException()
 + getMessage() : String
}

class TooScaredToMoveException {
 + TooScaredToMoveException(name: String)
}

class MissedTrainException {
 + MissedTrainException(message: String)
}

' Наследование исключений
FailedToBoardWagonException --|> RuntimeException
TooScaredToMoveException --|> RuntimeException
MissedTrainException --|> RuntimeException
IceCreamDepletedException --|> Exception

' Интерфейсы
interface Eatable {
 + eat(iceCream : IceCream) : void throws IceCreamDepletedException
}

interface Movable {
 + move() : void
}

interface Remember {
 + remember(moment : Event) : void
}

interface Runnable {
 + run(destination : Place) : void
}

interface Talkable {
 + say(message : String) : void
}

' Перечисления
enum State {
 OVERWHELMED
 CALM
 SCARED
 EXCITED
 REGULAR
}

enum Place {
 STATION
 WAGON
 HIGHWAY
 UNKNOWN

 - description : String
 + Place(description : String)
 + toString() : String
}

enum Flavour {
 UNKNOWN
 CHOCOLATE
 VANILLA
 STRAWBERRY
}

enum Event {
 CAR
 LOCOMOTIVE
 CRASH
}

' Абстрактный класс Person
abstract class Person {
 - name : String
 - place : Place
 - state : State
 - events : List<Event>
 
 + Person(name : String, place : Place, state : State)
 + getName() : String
 + getPlace() : Place
 + getState() : State
 + setState(state : State) : void
 + setPlace(place : Place) : void
 + addEvent(event : Event) : void
 + jump() : void
 + getEvents() : List<Event>
 + reactToEvent(event : Event) : void
 + assistJump(person : Person) : void
 + equals(o : Object) : boolean
 + hashCode() : int
 + toString() : String
}

' Наследники Person
class Pestryenkiy {
 - iceCreams : List<IceCream>
 + Pestryenkiy(name : String, place : Place, state : State, events : List<Event>, iceCreams : List<IceCream>)
 + eat(iceCream : IceCream) : void throws IceCreamDepletedException
 + say(message : String) : void
 + reactToEvent(event : Event) : void
 + assistJump(person : Person) : void
}

class Knopochka {
 + Knopochka(name : String, place : Place, state : State, events : List<Event>)
 + remember(moment : Event) : void
 + reactToEvent(event : Event) : void
 + assistJump(person : Person) : void
}

class Neznaika {
 + Neznaika(name : String, place : Place, state : State, events : List<Event>)
 + run(destination : Place) : void
 + say(message : String) : void
 + reactToEvent(event : Event) : void
 + assistJump(person : Person) : void
}

' Реализация интерфейсов
Pestryenkiy --|> Eatable
Pestryenkiy --|> Talkable
Knopochka --|> Remember
Neznaika --|> Runnable
Neznaika --|> Talkable
Train --|> Movable

' Наследование от Person
Pestryenkiy --|> Person
Knopochka --|> Person
Neznaika --|> Person

' Класс IceCream
class IceCream {
 - flavour : Flavour
 + IceCream(flavour : Flavour)
 + toString() : String
}

' Класс Train
class Train {
 - name : String
 + Train(name : String)
 + separate() : void
 + move() : void
}

' Ассоциации
Pestryenkiy --> IceCream : имеет список
Pestryenkiy --> Flavour : использует
Person --> State : использует
Person --> Place : использует
Person --> Event : имеет список
Knopochka --> Event : реагирует на
Neznaika --> Event : реагирует на
Train --> Place : использует

@enduml",
